{"tid":2451675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：無薪假是為資方分攤經濟風險 否則需裁減人手 政府無意干預","createTime":"2021-03-18T09:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T11:46:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"497432491e9172fab0035d9feb44125821aed503","tid":2451675,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"羅致光稱無薪假是「職位共享」文化 但政府無計劃推廣<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，飽受勞工界批評的無薪假，正是「職位共享」的文化，但政府無計劃推廣「職位共享」的文化。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光於立法會會議再提及對無薪假的看法，重申如果企業安排僱員每星期放一至兩天無薪假，就有如讓5名僱員分享3至4個人的職位，否則企業就要裁減兩至四成員工。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他又認為，失業情況於去年12月達到高峰，隨後在今年1至2月回落，相信只要控制疫情餘波及市民繼續接種疫苗，可以稍為樂觀地認為經濟會好轉，失業情況亦有機會改善。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581327-20210318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581327-20210318.htm&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2X0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=3bb25958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581327-20210318.htm&h=6e44fd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581327-20210318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"06f0648b8ef24f0bdea432ff131aeb8757f986e0","tid":2451675,"uid":68689,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"又唔見你份人工同我地共享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e7a8d3e6bfb28fe0d3c8a0ace7cb84be4aa530","tid":2451675,"uid":12412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"做老細有政府比錢出糧，反而打工比人炒失業就借錢比你，還唔到攪你信貸評級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef94396eff2e835034c03f01677f831f5f158bc","tid":2451675,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"就快會話無薪工作係無可耐何，否則要裁員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98871038646165a13733fff5a019f4221248b5d2","tid":24